1. download these all files as a ZIP file

2. install python
3. open start menu
4. right click on python 
5. select open file location 
6. right click on selected file
7. open file location
8. open scripts folder
9. type cmd on the address bar
10. type or paste all commands on the requirment text document 

11. extract the downloaded zip file
12. type CMD on the address bar
13. type the command PY base_code.py
14. it will run correctly if you installed old pip programs
